                        <seg type="rubrication">Divine names (name of the Virgin Mary in Text I-4);
                           titles and numbers of the Pss. and Canticles; numbers of Songs; title of
                           Texts I-2, I-3 and I-5; title and incipit of the daily readings of Text
                           I-4; name and traditional interpretation of the first letter, Aleph, in
                           Ps. 118; elements of the punctuation signs; Ethiopic numerals or their
                           elements.
 
 A few lines (alternating with black lines) on the
                           incipit page of Texts I-1 and I-4.</seg>
